title: 185: Don't expect us to bring a stick to a gun fight
description: I has been suggested that Mind Pump has been a little negative as of late. Let's just say the anger has been building. There are "big guns" in the fitness arena with huge influence absolutely spreading BS advice and selling bogus products to the unsuspecting masses. Sal, Adam, Justin and Doug take the mission of exposing the charlatans and spreading raw fitness truth to the masses very seriously. Please subscribe, rate and review this show! Learn more about Mind Pump at www.mindpumpradio.com
